Class SpaceFomFederateAmbassador

java.lang.Object
hla.rti1516e.NullFederateAmbassador
io.github.vega.core.SpaceFomFederateAmbassador
All Implemented Interfaces:
hla.rti1516e.FederateAmbassador
public class SpaceFomFederateAmbassador extends hla.rti1516e.NullFederateAmbassador
The federate ambassador used by Vega simulations. It simply redirects all operations to the HLACallbackManager and does not perform any actual tasks of its own.
Since:
1.0.0
Author:
Hridyanshu Aatreya
